    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "The true wife and mother ... will perform her duties with dignity and cheerfulness, not considering it degrading to do with her own hands whatever it is necessary to do in a well-ordered household.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">2<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"ST 9-9-1886\" data-link=\"820.7459\">The Signs of the Times, September 9, 1886</span>.</span></a></sup>",
