    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Mothers who sigh for a missionary field have one at hand in their own home circle.... Are not the souls of her own children of as much value as the souls of the heathen? With what care and tenderness should she watch their growing minds and connect God with all their thoughts! Who can do this as well as a loving, God-fearing mother?<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">4<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 43, 1900\" data-link=\"14065.7577001\">Manuscript 43, 1900</span>.</span></a></sup>",
